comment.body:
Unfortunately, the reported issue does not satisfy our [filters policy](https://kb.adguard.com/en/general/adguard-filter-policy). The website has low visitors. 
Please, add this rule to the User Rules:
```
androiddigger.de#$#body > div.dialog-widget[id^="elementor-popup-modal-"] { display: none !important; }
androiddigger.de#$#body { overflow: auto !important; }
```
